      "firm_id": "sybil_25",
      "description": "Presenting an automobile of uncompromising caliber, preserved in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained to ensure both its aesthetic and mechanical integrity remain peerless. The exterior retains a deep, factory-original luster, complemented by a pristine, smoke-free interior that reflects a standard of care rarely encountered in the secondary market. For the discerning driver who demands excellence, this specimen offers a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle indistinguishable from its original delivery state.",
